title: Huw Lloyd-Langton & Technicians of Spaceship Hawkwind - Hawkfest
description:
HAWKFEST 2007
Donnington Park Farmhouse	
Sunday 18th June 2007

LINEAGE FOR ALL RECORDINGS ON THIS DISC;
Stereo &#039;Stealth&#039; Microphones > Iriver H340 (Rockboxed) WAV > USB transfer to PC > Soundforge (fade in/out & eqs) > TLH (SBE fixes & FLAC conversion)

These 2 sets flowed into one another on the the night, so that&#039;s how I&#039;m uploading them.
The recordings of Huw & TOSH will run seamlessly together if played consecutively (either burnt on disc or in your preferred media player)
